%20Aditya-L1%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cnthe%20first%20space-based%20Indian%20observatory%20to%20study%20the%20Sun%20%E2%98%80%EF%B8%8F%2C%20is%20scheduled%20for%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9F%97%93%EF%B8%8FSeptember%202%2C%202023%2C%20at%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9F%95%9B11%3A50%20Hrs.%20IST%20from%20Sriharikota.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnCitizens%20are%20invited%20to%20witness%20the%20launch%20from%20the%20Launch%20View%20Gallery%20at%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbjhM5mZNrx%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbjhM5mZNrx%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1696097793616793910%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2028%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aditya-L1%20mission%2C%20aimed%20at%20studying%20the%20Sun%20from%20an%20orbit%20around%20the%20L1%2C%20would%20carry%20seven%20payloads%20to%20observe%20the%20photosphere%2C%20chromosphere%20and%20the%20outermost%20layers%20of%20the%20Sun%2C%20the%20corona%2C%20in%20different%20wavebands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya-L1%20is%20a%20fully%20indigenous%20effort%20with%20the%20participation%20of%20national%20institutions%2C%20an%20ISRO%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20science%20objectives%20of%20the%20Aditya-L1%20mission%20are%3A%20Study%20of%20Solar%20upper%20atmospheric%20(chromosphere%20and%20corona)%20dynamics%3B%20Study%20of%20chromospheric%20and%20coronal%20heating%2C%20physics%20of%20the%20partially%20ionised%20plasma%2C%20initiation%20of%20the%20coronal%20mass%20ejections%2C%20and%20flares%3B%20Observe%20the%20in-situ%20particle%20and%20plasma%20environment%20providing%20data%20for%20the%20study%20of%20particle%20dynamics%20from%20the%20Sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20include%20Physics%20of%20solar%20corona%20and%20its%20heating%20mechanism%3B%20Diagnostics%20of%20the%20coronal%20and%20coronal%20loops%20plasma%3A%20Temperature%2C%20velocity%20and%20density%3B%20Development%2C%20dynamics%20and%20origin%20of%20CMEs%3B%20Identify%20the%20sequence%20of%20processes%20that%20occur%20at%20multiple%20layers%20(chromosphere%2C%20base%20and%20extended%20corona)%20which%20eventually%20leads%20to%20solar%20eruptive%20events%3B%20Magnetic%20field%20topology%20and%20magnetic%20field%20measurements%20in%20the%20solar%20corona%3B%20Drivers%20for%20space%20weather%20(origin%2C%20composition%20and%20dynamics%20of%20solar%20wind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20instruments%20of%20Aditya-L1%20are%20tuned%20to%20observe%20the%20solar%20atmosphere%2C%20mainly%20the%20chromosphere%20and%20corona.%20In-situ%20instruments%20will%20observe%20the%20local%20environment%20at%20L1.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693220640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F9mjuu79o_aditya-l1_625x300_28_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisros-solar-mission-aditya-l-1-to-be-launched-on-this-date-4336180%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aditya-L1%20is%20a%20fully%20indigenous%20effort%20with%20the%20participation%20of%20national%20institutions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisros-solar-mission-aditya-l-1-to-be-launched-on-this-date-4336180%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisros-solar-mission-aditya-l-1-to-be-launched-on-this-date-4336180%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisros-solar-mission-aditya-l-1-to-be-launched-on-this-date-4336180%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japan%20Warns%20China%20After%20Stones%20Thrown%20At%20Embassy%20Over%20Nuke%20Water%20Release%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJapan's%20Prime%20Minister%20Fumio%20Kishida%20hit%20out%20at%20Beijing%20on%20Monday%20over%20what%20he%20said%20were%20instances%20of%20stones%20being%20thrown%20at%20diplomatic%20missions%20and%20schools%20in%20China%2C%20following%20the%20release%20of%20wastewater%20from%20the%20Fukushima%20nuclear%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20China%20banned%20all%20seafood%20imports%20from%20its%20neighbour%20after%20Japan%20began%20releasing%20cooling%20water%20from%20the%20stricken%20Fukushima%20plant%20in%20an%20operation%20that%20Tokyo%20and%20the%20UN's%20nuclear%20watchdog%20have%20said%20is%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Japanese%20businesses%20ranging%20from%20bakeries%20to%20aquariums%20have%20received%20reportedly%20thousands%20of%20sometimes%20abusive%20crank%20calls%20from%20Chinese%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20numerous%20harassment%20calls%20believed%20to%20originate%20from%20China%20and%20instances%20of%20stones%20being%20thrown%20into%20the%20Japanese%20embassy%20and%20Japanese%20schools.%20It%20must%20be%20said%20these%20are%20regrettable%2C%26quot%3B%20Fumio%20Kishida%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20summoned%20the%20Chinese%20ambassador%20to%20Japan%20today%20and%20strongly%20urged%20him%20to%20call%20on%20Chinese%20people%20to%20act%20in%20a%20calm%20and%20responsible%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20Fumio%20Kishida%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20came%20after%20Japan%20said%20it%20was%20heightening%20security%20at%20its%20diplomatic%20missions%20and%20schools%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETokyo%20over%20the%20weekend%20told%20its%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20nationals%20living%20in%20China%20to%20keep%20a%20low%20profile%20and%20not%20to%20speak%20Japanese%20loudly%20in%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Foreign%20Minister%20Masataka%20Okano%20told%20ambassador%20Wu%20Jianghao%20that%20China%20should%20properly%20inform%20the%20public%20%26quot%3Brather%20than%20unnecessarily%20raising%20people's%20concerns%20by%20providing%20information%20that%20is%20not%20based%20on%20scientific%20evidence%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20users%20in%20China%20have%20posted%20recordings%20and%20videos%20of%20the%20nuisance%20calls%2C%20some%20of%20which%20have%20attracted%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20likes%20and%20a%20large%20number%20of%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20start%20of%20the%20discharge...%20there%20have%20been%20numerous%20phone%20calls%20and%20other%20harassment%20regarding%20the%20discharge%20that%20are%20suspected%20of%20originating%20from%20China.%20The%20situation%20has%20not%20improved%20since%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Okano%20told%20Wu%20Jianghao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20number%20of%20similar%20incidents%20are%20also%20happening%20in%20China%20against%20Japan-related%20facilities.%20This%20is%20extremely%20regrettable%20and%20we%20are%20deeply%20concerned%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan%20has%20begun%20releasing%20more%20than%20500%20Olympic%20swimming%20pools'%20worth%20of%20wastewater%20from%20Fukushima%20into%20the%20Pacific%2C%2012%20years%20after%20a%20tsunami%20knocked%20out%20three%20reactors%20in%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20worst%20atomic%20accidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlant%20operator%20TEPCO%20says%20all%20radioactive%20elements%20have%20been%20filtered%20out%20except%20for%20tritium%2C%20levels%20of%20which%20are%20within%20safe%20limits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETest%20results%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20discharge%20have%20confirmed%20this%2C%20according%20to%20Japanese%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693220640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fr7p1sqbg_japan-fukushima-plant-reuters-_625x300_24_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapan-warns-china-after-stones-thrown-at-embassy-over-fukushima-water-release-4336182%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Japan's%20Prime%20Minister%20Fumio%20Kishida%20hit%20out%20at%20Beijing%20on%20Monday%20over%20what%20he%20said%20were%20instances%20of%20stones%20being%20thrown%20at%20diplomatic%20missions%20and%20schools%20in%20China%2C%20following%20the%20release%20of%20wastewater%20from%20the%20Fukushima%20nuclear%20plant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapan-warns-china-after-stones-thrown-at-embassy-over-fukushima-water-release-4336182%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapan-warns-china-after-stones-thrown-at-embassy-over-fukushima-water-release-4336182%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapan-warns-china-after-stones-thrown-at-embassy-over-fukushima-water-release-4336182%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Legacy%20of%20Des%20Raj%20Kali%2C%20Renowned%20Writer%2C%20Journalist%20and%20Literature%20Icon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28153910%2Fimage-1260-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJalandhar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Noted%20Punjabi%20writer%2C%20journalist%2C%20critic%20and%20social%20thinker%2C%20Des%20Raj%20Kali%2C%20who%20took%20literature%20from%20the%20roots%20of%20lesser-known%20villages%20of%20Punjab%20to%20the%20global%20stage%2C%20passed%20away%20on%20August%2027%20in%20Chandigarh.%20He%20was%2051.%20He%20was%20suffering%20from%20liver%20cirrhosis%20and%20was%20admitted%20to%20Chandigarh%E2%80%99s%20PGI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20cremation%20will%20take%20place%20on%20August%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKali%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20wife%20and%20three%20children%20%E2%80%93%20a%20son%2C%20Karan%2C%20and%20two%20daughters%2C%20Shivalika%20and%20Zunish.%20He%20hailed%20from%20Mithapur%20village%20in%20Jalandhar%2C%20which%20is%20also%20famous%20for%20hockey%20stars%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKali%20wrote%20about%20Dalit%20life%20and%20injustices%20face%20through%20his%20own%20experiences%20of%20the%20society%20that%20he%20grew%20up%20in.%20The%20author%20would%20often%20say%20that%20he%20could%20withstand%20the%20adversities%20of%20life%20as%20he%20came%20from%20a%20%E2%80%98culturally%20elite%20Dalit%20background%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20the%20Dalit%20heartland%20of%20Punjab%2C%20the%20Doaba%20region%2C%20Kali%E2%80%99s%20work%20was%20influenced%20by%20the%20teachings%20of%20Sufi%20saints%20who%20thronged%20the%20villages%20and%20deserts%20of%20undivided%20rural%20Punjab%2C%20and%20iconic%20Dalit%20writers%20Lal%20Singh%20Dil%20and%20Sant%20Gulab%20Das.%20The%20originality%20in%20his%20work%20brought%20a%20new%20turn%20in%20Punjabi%20story%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKali%20explored%20anti-caste%20struggles%2C%20culture%2C%20tradition%20and%20literature%20in%20the%20form%20of%20novels%20and%20short%20stories.%20He%20also%20presented%20research%20papers%20in%20renowned%20universities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20journalist%20Pal%20Singh%20Nauli%2C%20who%20knew%20Kali%20for%20over%2030%20years%2C%20shared%20some%20lesser-known%20facts%20about%20the%20writer%E2%80%99s%20life%2C%20which%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20him.%20%E2%80%9CKali%20grew%20up%20in%20an%20environment%20where%20all%20that%20he%20saw%20was%20an%20unjust%20society%2C%20where%20Dalits%20were%20meant%20to%20perform%20menial%20jobs%20only.%20His%20father%20used%20to%20pick%20the%20dead%20animals%20on%20his%20bicycle%20in%20the%20village%20and%20skin%20them.%20Even%20as%20a%20child%2C%20Kali%20used%20to%20accompany%20his%20father%20to%20this%20work.%20He%20would%20often%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EAsi%20sadiyan%20to%20uppercaste%20loka%20di%20gulami%20karde%20a%20rahe%20a%2C%20asi%20es%20baare%20kyu%20na%20gal%20kariye%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20(We%20have%20been%20the%20slaves%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20people.%20Why%20should%20we%20not%20talk%20about%20this%3F)'%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20words%20of%20one%20of%20his%20close%20friends%2C%20Makhan%20Mann%2C%20a%20retired%20Punjab%20revenue%20officer%20who%20also%20took%20to%20writing%2C%20Kali%20knew%20how%20to%20read%20a%20book.%20%E2%80%9COur%20friendship%20is%2035%20years%20old.%20Kali%20used%20to%20address%20me%20as%20Mann%20Bhaji.%20We%20used%20to%20write%20stories%20together.%20It%20was%20his%20heart%20of%20gold%2C%20like%20a%20fakir%3Cem%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20earned%20him%20love%20and%20respect%20from%20people.%20He%20was%20a%20writer%2C%20poet%2C%20journalist%2C%20historian%2C%20critic%2C%20philosopher%20and%20a%20wonderful%20human%20being.%20%3Cem%3EOh%20Daler%20si%3C%2Fem%3E%20(He%20was%20a%20fearless%20person).%20He%20never%20took%20caste%20as%20a%20caste.%20He%20would%20rather%20talk%20about%20the%20problem%20and%20maintain%20a%20scientific%20approach%20to%20it.%20He%20used%20to%20study%20deeply%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKali%E2%80%99s%20writings%20and%20career%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMann%20shared%20how%20Kali%E2%80%99s%20novel%20%3Cem%3EShanti%20Parav%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20published%20by%20Orient%20Blackswan%2C%20remained%20one%20of%20his%20bestselling%20books.%20The%20book%20is%20based%20on%20post-colonial%20Punjab%20from%20a%20Dalit%20person%E2%80%99s%20perspective.%20It%20talked%20about%20governance%2C%20violence%20and%20peace%20through%20three%20retired%20Dalit%20characters.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20days%2C%20he%20was%20writing%20a%20novel%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3EDukh%20Kade%20Budhe%20nai%20Hunde%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Sorrow%20never%20gets%20old).%20He%20was%20also%20planning%20to%20start%20a%20fortnightly%20newspaper%20but%20we%20never%20knew%20that%20he%20would%20leave%20us%20so%20all%20of%20sudden%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKali%E2%80%99s%20short%20story%20collections%20include%20%3Cem%3EKath%20Kali%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Stories%20of%20Kali)%2C%20%3Cem%3EFakiri%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Mendicancy)%20and%20%3Cem%3EYahan%20Chai%20Achi%20Nahi%20Banti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Good%20Tea%20is%20Not%20Served%20Here).%20His%20novels%20are%20%3Cem%3EAntheen%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Eternal)%2C%20%3Cem%3EPrathan%20Pauran%3C%2Fem%3E%20(First%20Puran)%2C%20%3Cem%3EShanti%20Parav%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EShehar%20Vich%20Sahn%20Honn%20da%20Matlab%3C%2Fem%3E%20(What%20it%20Means%20to%20be%20a%20Bull%20in%20the%20Town).%20He%20also%20published%20research%20papers%20on%20the%20literature%20and%20culture%20of%20Punjab%20and%20gender%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20research%20on%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Ghadar%20movement%20in%20the%20form%20of%20four%20books%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3EUngauley%20Nayak%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Forgotten%20Heroes)%2C%20%3Cem%3EGadri%20Banta%20Singh%20Sanghwal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EGadri%20Bhai%20Randhir%20Singh%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%3Cem%3E%20Gadri%20Ram%20Saran%20Dass%20Talwar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20remains%20the%20best%20collection%20of%20historic%20work%20in%20Ghadar%20literature.%20Kali%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20Desh%20Bhagat%20Yadgaar%20Committee%2C%20Jalandhar%2C%20a%20platform%20dedicated%20to%20the%20Ghadar%20movement%2C%20and%20was%20often%20spotted%20at%20the%20committee%20office%20sharing%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%20with%20like-minded%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKali%E2%80%99s%20work%20was%20celebrated%20in%20major%20festivals%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20including%20the%20prestigious%20Jaipur%20Literature%20Festival%2C%20Samanvay%20Samagam%20and%20at%20renowned%20foreign%20universities.%20The%20writer%20had%20the%20honour%20of%20presenting%20his%20work%20at%20Monash%20University%2C%20Melbourne%20on%20the%20125th%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20to%20trace%20common%20ground%20between%20the%20people%20from%20the%20Dalit%20and%20Australian%20tribal%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20novel%20%3Cem%3EShanti%20Parav%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20celebrated%20at%20the%20Chandigarh%20Literature%20Festival%20in%202013.%20He%20also%20edited%20the%20literary%20quarterly%20%3Cem%3ELakeer%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20directed%20a%20documentary%20%3Cem%3EKitey%20Mil%20Ve%20Mahi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20going%20to%20the%20Jaipur%20Literature%20Fest%20in%202016%2C%20Kali%2C%20while%20talking%20about%20the%20history%20of%20Dalit%20literature%20and%20its%20writers%2C%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CDalit%20and%20Punjabi%20literature%20have%20their%20roots%20in%20the%20Buddhist%20and%20Sufi%20philosophy%20with%20genesis%20through%20%E2%80%98Nath%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Yogis%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20Punjabi%20culture.%20While%20Dalit%20literature%20was%20philosophical%2C%20the%20Hindi%20and%20the%20Marathi%20writers%20like%20Jyoti%20Rao%20Phule%20and%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20were%20politically%20influenced.%20That%20is%20why%20I%20would%20talk%20about%20iconic%20Dalit%20writers%20like%20Gulab%20Dass%2C%20Peero%20Preman%2C%20Wazir%20Singh%20and%20Nurung%20Devi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20would%20also%20share%20that%20the%20folk%20and%20oral%20Punjabi%20literature%20that%20he%20learnt%20through%20his%20ancestors%20laid%20the%20foundation%20of%20his%20writings.%20Kali%20also%20remained%20associated%20with%20All%20India%20Radio%20(AIR)%20in%20Jalandhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20award-winning%20author%20started%20his%20career%20by%20working%20for%20Punjabi%20newspapers%20%3Cem%3ENawan%20Zamana%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EDesh%20Sewak.%3C%2Fem%3E%20He%20was%20the%20resident%20editor%20of%20the%20magazine%20section%20of%20%3Cem%3EDainik%20Bhaskar%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20Jalandhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost%20COVID-19%2C%20Kali%20was%20running%20his%20own%20YouTube%20channel%20%3Cem%3EBarqtanWebTV%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20platform%20where%20he%20discussed%20caste%20issues%2C%20culture%2C%20tradition%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Punjabi%20and%20Punjabiyat%20and%20human-interest%20issues.%20He%20described%20his%20channel%20as%20%E2%80%98Dua%E2%80%99%20and%20would%20share%20his%20web%20channel%20videos%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20journalists%20and%20like-minded%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20vocal%20against%20atrocities%20on%20the%20people%20from%20the%20minority%20communities%20and%20the%20Adivasis.%20Recently%2C%20when%20the%20video%20of%20a%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20leader%20urinating%20on%20the%20face%20of%20an%20Adivasi%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20went%20viral%2C%20Kali%20held%20a%20special%20programme%2C%20holding%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20the%20right-wing%20groups%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKali%E2%80%99s%20personal%20life%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20Rajesh%20Bagha%2C%20who%20was%20Kali%E2%80%99s%20close%20friend%2C%20shared%20some%20interesting%20facts%20about%20his%20personal%20life.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20many%20people%20know%20that%20Kali%20had%20an%20inter-caste%20but%20arranged%20marriage.%20His%20wife%20was%20a%20Brahmin.%20It%20was%20because%20of%20Kali%E2%80%99s%20nature%20that%20his%20father-in-law%20decided%20to%20approach%20his%20family%20for%20marriage.%20He%20was%20energetic%2C%20a%20carefree%20person%20and%20someone%20who%20would%20deeply%20feel%20for%20his%20friends.%20It%20is%20a%20huge%20loss%20for%20us%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBagha%20said%20Kali%20was%20well-read.%20He%20would%20delve%20deep%20into%20his%20characters.%20%E2%80%9CKali%20used%20to%20live%20in%20his%20characters.%20Often%20when%20we%20met%20over%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%2C%20we%20would%20notice%20him%20deeply%20lost%20in%20his%20thoughts.%20He%20would%20share%20that%20I%20am%20writing%20a%20story%20and%20the%20character%20was%20living%20with%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20friend%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20who%20is%20an%20independent%20journalist%2C%20was%20so%20much%20influenced%20by%20Kali%E2%80%99s%20work%20that%20after%20reading%20one%20of%20his%20pieces%20in%20%3Cem%3EDainik%20Bhaskar%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202010%2C%20he%20went%20to%20meet%20him.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20how%20I%20got%20a%20friend%20and%20a%20philosopher%20for%20life.%20Kali%E2%80%99s%20office%20near%20Jalandhar%20Doordarshan%20Kendra%20remained%20our%20sought-after%20destination%2C%20where%20our%20conversations%20ranged%20from%20life%2C%20society%2C%20politics%2C%20national%20and%20international%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20shared%20that%20apart%20from%20his%20writings%2C%20Kali%20was%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20rising%20communal%20hatred%20and%20attacks%20on%20the%20minorities%2C%20particularly%20Muslims.%20%E2%80%9CRecently%2C%20when%20communal%20tensions%20flared%20up%20in%20Nuh%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Kali%20pointed%20out%20that%20this%20was%20yet%20another%20attempt%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20divert%20people%E2%80%99s%20attention%20from%20the%20incident%20in%20Manipur.%20He%20would%20feel%20the%20miseries%20of%20the%20minorities%20and%20often%20convey%20perturbed%20thoughts%20about%20the%20same.%20In%20him%2C%20we%20have%20lost%20a%20fine%20journalist%2C%20thinker%2C%20writer%2C%20and%20a%20friend%20for%20life.%20That%20office%20and%20our%20evenings%20will%20never%20be%20the%20same%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693220405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28153910%2Fimage-1260-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-legacy-of-des-raj-kali-renowned-writer-journalist-and-literature-icon%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kali%20explored%20anti-caste%20struggles%2C%20culture%2C%20tradition%20and%20literature%20in%20the%20form%20of%20novels%20and%20short%20stories.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-legacy-of-des-raj-kali-renowned-writer-journalist-and-literature-icon%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Children%20have%20right%20to%20clean%20environment%20-%20report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3