2bc2d0019911df8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222387%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKirill%20Bigai%2C%20the%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Preply.%3Cp%3EPreply%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFounded%20in%202012%2C%20Preply%20offers%20virtual%20live%20language%20tutoring%20for%20over%2050%20languages.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20founders%20started%20Preply%20after%20they%20moved%20from%20Ukraine%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPreply%20recently%20raised%20%2470%20million%20in%20a%20Series%20C%20extension%20round%20led%20by%20Horizon%20Capital.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20Preply%20CEO%20Kirill%20Bigai%20and%20his%20future%20cofounders%20Dmytro%20Voloshyn%20and%20Sergey%20Lukyanov%20moved%20from%20Ukraine%20to%20Boston%20for%20work.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Bigai%20felt%20like%20his%20English%20proficiency%20wasn't%20where%20he%20wanted%20it%20to%20be.%20%26quot%3BOn%20paper%2C%20I%20was%20intermediate%2C%20but%20I%20was%20struggling%20to%20connect%20with%20people%20for%20business%2C%20%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20with%20his%20English%2C%20Bigai%20found%20an%20online%20tutor%20who%20taught%20classes%20from%20Texas%20via%20Skype.%20The%20two%20hit%20it%20off%20and%20he%20could%20tell%20that%20his%20English%20skills%20were%20improving.%20He%20started%20to%20see%20the%20potential%20for%20online%20language%20tutoring%20as%20a%20viable%20business%20model%2C%20since%20online%20lessons%20were%20cheaper%20than%20in-person%20lessons%20and%20class%20schedules%20were%20more%20flexible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%20of%202012%2C%20Bigai%2C%20Voloshyn%20and%20Lukyanov%20founded%20the%20online%20language%20learning%20startup%20Preply.%20In%20the%20decade%20since%20its%20founding%2C%20Preply%20has%20grown%20to%20500%20employees%20of%2060%20different%20nationalities%2C%20with%20over%2035%2C000%20online%20tutors%2C%20and%20offices%20in%20Barcelona%2C%20Boston%2C%20and%20Kyiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Preply%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globenewswire.com%2Fnews-release%2F2023%2F07%2F19%2F2707255%2F0%2Fen%2FUkrainian-Founded-Preply-raises-70m-to-Supercharge-Language-Tutors-with-AI.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%20a%20%2470%20million%20Series%20C%20extension%20round%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20combination%20of%20debt%20and%20equity%20led%20by%20Horizon%20Capital.%20Reach%20Capital%2C%20Hoxton%20Ventures%20and%20Owl%20Ventures%2C%20which%20led%20its%20previous%20%2450%20million%20Series%20C%20in%202022%2C%20also%20participated.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Preply's%20more%20prominent%20competitors%20include%20apps%20like%20Duolingo%20or%20other%20virtual%20tutoring%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhired-at-amazon-after-learning-english-with-app-cambly-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECambly%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20only%20offers%20English%20lessons.%20The%20global%20language%20learning%20market%20was%20estimated%20to%20be%20valued%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gminsights.com%2Findustry-analysis%2Flanguage-learning-market%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%2452%20billion%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20growing%20in%202022.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreply%20offers%20classes%20in%2050%20languages%2C%20and%20tutors%20are%20independent%20contractors%20who%20set%20their%20own%20rates%20and%20schedules.%20While%20consumer%20language%20learners%20use%20Preply%2C%20many%20of%20the%20startup's%20customers%20come%20from%20enterprise%20partnerships%20with%20over%20200%20companies%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdatadog-ceo-developer-platform-company-cybersecurity-it-finance-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EDatadog%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-a-job-at-bain-global-head-recruiting-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBain%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20back%20when%20Preply%20was%20founded%2C%20the%20team%20found%20it%20hard%20to%20even%20recruit%20tutors%20to%20teach%20online%20classes%2C%20let%20alone%20attract%20investors%2C%20Bigai%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20contacting%20tutors%20who%20had%20never%20done%20online%20classes%2C%20and%20they%20were%20suspicious%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20though%2C%20more%20investors%20became%20familiar%20with%20Preply's%20model.%20In%202015%2C%20the%20team%20took%20a%20meeting%20with%20a%20well-known%20investor%20in%20Berlin%2C%20who%20told%20the%20founders%20he%20had%20heard%20of%20the%20company%20because%20he%20was%20using%20it%20to%20learn%20Czech%20so%20he%20could%20speak%20to%20his%20wife%20in%20her%20native%20language%2C%20said%20Bigai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Preply%20moved%20on%20from%20being%20bootstrapped.%20It%20first%20took%20venture%20funding%20in%202020%2C%20Bigai%20said.%20After%20this%20most%20recent%20%2470%20million%20Series%20C%20extension%2C%20Preply's%20total%20funding%20sits%20at%20around%20%24170%20million%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpitchbook.com%2Fprofiles%2Fcompany%2F91286-74%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EPitchBook%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20this%20latest%20infusion%20of%20cash%20will%20help%20develop%20more%20products%20that%20use%20generative%20AI%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hadn't%20done%20a%20large%20language%20learning%20investment%20yet%2C%20which%20was%20surprising%20as%20an%20edtech%20fund%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Reach%20Capital%20partner%20James%20Kim%2C%20who%20handled%20Preply's%20Series%20C%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fedtech-vc-firm-reach-capital-raises-education-startup-investing-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EReach%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20category%20that's%20ripe%20for%20tech%20enablement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20successful%20fundraising%20comes%20after%20a%20difficult%20year%20personally%20for%20the%20Preply%20team.%20The%20cofounders%20of%20Preply%20are%20all%20Ukrainian%2C%20and%20Preply%20had%20over%20115%20employees%20in%20Kyiv%20when%20Russia%20invaded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-tech-startups-help-employees-in-ukraine-grammarly-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EUkraine%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%202022.%20Bigai%20and%20his%20cofounders%20established%20a%20team%20effort%2C%20called%20%26quot%3Bno%20Prepler%20left%20behind%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20helped%20colleagues%20find%20accommodations%20for%20the%20first%20few%20months%20outside%20of%20Kyiv%20and%20get%20cash%20from%20their%20salaries%20up%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20Preply's%20Ukrainian%20employees%20are%20accounted%20for%20to%20date%2C%20and%20100%20have%20returned%20to%20Kyiv.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20big%20inspiration%20to%20see%20people%20working%20on%20the%20team%2C%20despite%20what%20had%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20Bigai%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20forward%2C%20the%20biggest%20launch%20for%20Preply%20has%20been%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feducation-experts-teachers-generative-ai-chatgpt-classroom-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAI%20tutoring%20assistant%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20generate%20new%20customized%20lesson%20plans%20and%20exercises.%20But%20Bigai%20is%20clear%20that%20it%20will%20not%20replace%20the%20need%20for%20human%20language%20teachers.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20in%20a%20world%20where%20efficient%20online%20language%20learning%20is%20human%20led%20and%20supported%20by%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpreply-online-language-learning-ukraine-edtech-startup-2023-8%