Fabrice%20and%20Eve%20Ivara.%3Cp%3ECap%20Karoso%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFabrice%20and%20Eve%20Ivara%20bought%20a%20plot%20of%20land%20in%202017%20on%20the%20wild%20island%20of%20Sumba%20in%20Indonesia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20turned%20the%20land%20into%20a%20luxury%20resort%20that%20runs%20on%20solar%20power%20and%20has%20its%20own%20organic%20farm.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGuests%20can%20stay%20in%20suites%20and%20villas%20on%20the%20beach%20at%20Cap%20Karoso%20for%20up%20to%20%241%2C100%20a%20night.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Eve%20and%20Fabrice%20Ivara%20both%20hit%20a%20crossroads%20in%20their%20careers.%C2%A0She%20worked%20for%20Mo%C3%ABt%20Hennessy%20in%20marketing%2C%20and%20he%20was%20about%20to%20sell%20his%20company%20after%20working%20for%20KPMG.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20decided%20to%20leave%20their%20home%20in%20France%20and%20go%20on%20a%20two-month%20adventure%2C%20making%20stops%20along%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspain-real-estate-visa-remote-work-digital-nomad-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoast%20of%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-war-ukraine-phosphate-rock-electric-cars-norge-mining-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewilderness%20of%20Norway%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20flying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftourist-visa-bali-wealthy-digital-nomad-remote-work-10-years-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBali%2C%20Indonesia%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20dinner%20in%20Bali%20with%20some%20people%20they'd%20met%20during%20the%20trip%2C%20they%20were%20told%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweloveitwild.com%2Fsumba-indonesias-wild-west%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20island%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20should%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20they%20spoke%20about%20Sumba%2C%20they%20almost%20spoke%20of%20it%20in%20mythical%20tones.%20It%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%20movie%2C%20'The%20Beach%2C'%26quot%3B%20Eve%20Ivara%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20Fabrice%20Ivara%20was%20walking%20along%20the%20high%20street%20in%20Seminyak%20when%20he%20saw%20some%20property%20in%20Sumba%20advertised%20in%20a%20real-estate%20agent's%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20land%20wasn't%20expensive%2C%20so%20it%20caught%20our%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20Eve%20Ivara%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20we%20were%20about%20to%20return%20to%20France%2C%20my%20husband%20left%20his%20contact%20details%2C%20and%20they%20said%20they'd%20email%20us%20when%20plots%20of%20land%20became%20available.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20year%2C%20they%20purchased%20a%20plot%20of%20land%20in%20Sumba%20and%20began%20construction%20on%20a%20resort.%20Now%2C%20they%20run%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcapkaroso.com%2Fen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECap%20Karoso%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20they%20named%20after%20Karoso%20beach%20where%20it's%20situated%2C%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFalling%20in%20love%20with%20Sumba%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202016%2C%20Fabrice%20Ivara%20sold%20his%20company%2C%20and%20Eve%20launched%20her%20own%20consultancy%2C%20so%20they%20went%20to%20the%20Maldives%20to%20celebrate.%20On%20their%20way%20home%2C%20Fabrice%20received%20an%20email%20from%20the%20real-estate%20agent%20in%20Bali.%20They%20had%20a%209-hectare%20plot%20for%20sale%20on%20the%20coast%20in%20Sumba.%20As%20soon%20as%20they%20touched%20down%20in%20Paris%2C%20the%20couple%20repacked%20their%20suitcases%20and%20flew%20to%20see%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20arrived%20in%20Sumba%20for%20the%20first%20time%20during%20the%20rainy%20season.%20The%20road%20was%20destroyed%2C%20there%20was%20no%20internet%20connection%2C%20and%2C%20when%20they%20stepped%20out%20of%20the%20agent's%20car%20to%20view%20the%20land%20for%20sale%2C%20they%20were%20greeted%20with%20scrubland%2C%20rocks%2C%20and%20two%20palm%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20the%20couple%20immediately%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20untamed%20and%20undeveloped%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ocean%20was%20so%20blue%2C%20and%20there%20was%20this%20very%20gray%20sky%2C%26quot%3B%20Eve%20Ivara%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20looked%20like%20we'd%20reached%20the%20end%20of%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20put%20in%20an%20offer%2C%20and%20by%20February%202017%2C%20the%20plot%20was%20theirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEve%20Ivara%20said%20they%20wanted%20to%20do%20more%20than%20use%20the%20land%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-in-real-estate-buy-property-with-small-income-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestment%20property%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20want%20to%20just%20own%20the%20land%2C%20speculate%2C%20and%20sell%20it%20again%20because%20what%20would%20you%20gain%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20at%20a%20crossroads%2C%20and%20this%20would%20give%20us%20a%20chance%20to%20move%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20thought%20at%20first%20about%20opening%20a%20three-star%20hotel%2C%20as%20they%20could%20do%20this%20with%20their%20savings.%20But%20when%20Fabrice%20Ivara%20started%20to%20crunch%20the%20numbers%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20to%20make%20the%20project%20profitable%2C%20they%20would%20need%20to%20charge%20luxury%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20loved%20the%20food%20in%20Spain%2C%20the%20wilderness%20of%20Norway%2C%20and%20the%20friendly%20atmosphere%20of%20Bali%2C%20so%20Cap%20Karoso%20became%20a%20combination%20of%20all%20their%20adventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeeking%20funding%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20beach%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e8dd4db413420019a392ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20plot%20the%20Ivaras%20purchased.%3Cp%3ECap%20Karoso%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20four-level%20resort%20on%20the%20hillside%20by%20the%20beach%20in%20the%20most%20sustainable%20way%20possible.%20But%20installing%20a%20state-of-the-art%20water-treatment%20plant%20on%20a%20tropical%20island%20wouldn't%20come%20cheap%2C%20so%20they%20had%20to%20seek%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20they%20hired%20Gary%20Fell%2C%20a%20British%20architect%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgfabarchitects.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGFAB%20Architects%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Bali.%20Fell%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20space%20that%20fit%20into%20the%20natural%20environment.%20He%20created%20a%20modern%20hotel%20with%20many%20nods%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20island%2C%20including%20a%20spa%20cluster%20of%20wooden%20villas%20with%20statuesque%20Sumbanese%20roofs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20was%20working%20on%20the%20drawings%2C%20the%20couple%20flew%20to%20London%20and%20Singapore%20to%20speak%20with%20investors.%20While%20Eve%20Ivara%20was%20running%20her%20consultancy%2C%20her%20husband%20was%20working%20on%20Cap%20Karoso%20full%20time.%20In%20July%202018%2C%20they%20moved%20to%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20sunk%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20their%20savings%20into%20the%20project%20to%20show%20investors%20how%20dedicated%20they%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20just%20given%20birth%20to%20our%20daughter%20the%20month%20before%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20that%20nothing%20could%20stop%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Eve%20Ivara%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20to%20complete%20the%20multimillion-dollar%20fundraise%2C%20which%20involved%20investors%20such%20as%20an%20Indonesian%20property%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGetting%20permission%20from%20the%20locals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224128%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20couple%20speaking%20to%20a%20man%20in%20Sumba%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e8dceeb413420019a39223%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222752%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Ivaras%20at%20the%20approval%20ceremony.%3Cp%3ECap%20Karoso%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20they%20could%20start%20construction%20in%20October%202019%2C%20they%20needed%20to%20take%20part%20in%20an%20ancient%20religious%20ceremony%20where%20the%20local%20Marapu%20people%20asked%20the%20ancestors%20of%20the%20land%20for%20their%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShamans%20from%20the%20surrounding%20villages%20and%20600%20villagers%20gathered%20at%20Cap%20Karoso.%20The%20shamans%20carried%20out%20traditional%20dances%2C%20followed%20by%20long%20trancelike%20prayers%20in%20the%20Kodi%20dialect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20oldest%20shaman%20then%20pronounced%2C%20'The%20ancestors%20gave%20their%20agreement.%20Cap%20Karoso%20will%20be%20built%2C'%26quot%3B%20Eve%20Ivara%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20thanked%20the%20community%20in%20Indonesia's%20national%20language%20of%20Bahasa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20speak%20any%20of%20it%20at%20the%20time%2C%20so%20I%20learned%20my%20speech%20by%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20Eve%20Ivara%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFacing%20challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20villa%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e8de27bc26b400199009e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20villas.%3Cp%3ECap%20Karoso%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20a%20hotel%20on%20the%20island%20was%20a%20challenge%2C%20from%20navigating%20construction%20equipment%20down%20village%20roads%20to%20finding%20out%20that%20the%20ship%20containing%20their%20materials%20couldn't%20leave%20port%20because%20of%20bad%20weather.%20Eve%20Ivara%20said%20that%20once%20a%20boat%20would%20arrive%2C%20they%20might%20find%20that%20a%20supplier%20forgot%20to%20send%20half%20of%20the%20materials%2C%20which%20would%20mean%20a%20contractor%20couldn't%20start%20work%2C%20so%20they'd%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20dealt%20with%20a%20costly%20leveling%20mistake%20when%20the%20person%20they%20hired%20to%20measure%20the%20terrain%20calculated%20the%20angle%20incorrectly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEve%20Ivara%20said%20her%20favorite%20part%20was%20working%20with%20the%20local%20artisans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorking%20on%20this%20project%20was%20deliriously%20enjoyable%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20artisans%20really%20understood%20my%20brief%20each%20time%2C%20and%20they'd%20always%20surpass%20what%20I'd%20imagined.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20always%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20embed%20Sumbanese%20symbols%20in%20their%20design.%20The%20statement%20lobby%20artwork%20was%20inspired%20by%20her%20visit%20to%20a%20Sumbanese%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDealing%20with%20the%20pandemic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20farm%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e8deacb413420019a39503%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20farm.%3Cp%3ECap%20Karoso%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%202019%2C%20the%20couple%20started%20work%20on%20a%20farm%20by%20leasing%20a%203-hectare%20plot%20of%20land%20from%20a%20neighbor.%20Fabrice%20Ivara%20had%20met%20Philippe%20Guiglionda%2C%20a%20farm%20consultant%2C%20through%20a%20friend%20in%20Singapore%20and%20invited%20him%20to%20oversee%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20and%20progress%20on%20the%20hotel%20ground%20to%20a%20halt.%20The%20couple%20had%20to%20manage%20the%20project%20from%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20two-bedroom%20villa%20was%20finished%20in%202021%2C%20and%20this%20became%20the%20family's%20home%20in%20Sumba.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20to%20open%20all%20the%20units%20at%20once%2C%20but%2C%20of%20course%2C%20with%20COVID-19%20and%20its%20delays%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20open%20progressively%2C%26quot%3B%20Eve%20Ivara%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20started%20with%20a%20soft%20launch%20before%20they%20welcomed%20guests%20to%20each%20of%20their%2047%20suites%20and%2020%20villas%2C%20which%20cost%20between%20%24250%20and%20%241%2C100%20a%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20grand%20opening%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20bedroom%20in%20a%20resort%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e8ddcdbc26b40019900963%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221997%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20bedroom%20in%20one%20of%20the%20villas.%3Cp%3ECap%20Karoso%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20officially%20opened%20the%20hotel%20on%20March%2020.%20Thanks%20to%20Eve%20Ivara's%20marketing%20background%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coupdefourchette.fr%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eher%20husband's%20food%20blog%2C%20Coup%20De%20Fourchette%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Cap%20Karoso%20had%20already%20started%20to%20garner%20interest%20from%20Asian%20and%20European%20publications.%20Everyone%20was%20searching%20for%20an%20off-the-beaten-track%20destination%20after%20COVID-19%20lockdowns%20ended%2C%20and%20that's%20what%20Cap%20Karoso%20offered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20hired%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbirdtravelpr.com%2Fclients%2Fcap-karoso%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eluxury-travel%20public-relations%20company%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20work%20with%20the%20media%2C%20and%20Eve%20Ivara%20curated%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcap_karoso%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%20page%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designhotels.com%2Fhotels%2Findonesia%2Fsumba%2Fate-dalo%2Fcap-karoso%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epartnered%20with%20Design%20Hotels%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20they%20were%20both%20fans%20of%2C%20after%20meeting%20its%20vice%20president%20of%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20the%20Ivara%20family%20splits%20its%20time%20between%20Sumba%20and%20Singapore%20and%20relishes%20the%20role%20of%20hotelier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20guests%20have%20already%20done%20things%20we%20haven't%20yet%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20do%2C%20as%20we've%20been%20so%20busy%2C%26quot%3B%20Eve%20Ivara%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20still%20haven't%20surfed%2C%20and%20the%20only%20time%20I've%20laid%20down%20on%20the%20lounger%20was%20when%20I%20bought%20it%20in%20the%20factory.%20We're%20enjoying%20being%20part%20of%20someone%20else's%20memories.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-couple-created-cap-karoso-luxury-resort-sumba-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693213381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e8d8cfbc26b400199001e0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-couple-created-cap-karoso-luxury-resort-sumba-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fabrice%20and%20Eve%20Ivara%20saw%20land%20advertised%20on%20the%20island%20of%20Sumba%2C%20and%20they%20made%20an%20offer.%20Six%20years%20later%2C%20they%20opened%20a%20four-level%20resort%20called%20Cap%20Karoso.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Claire%20Turrell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-couple-created-cap-karoso-luxury-resort-sumba-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Archaeology%20of%20a%20Disaster%20in%20Shiv%20Baodi%2C%20Summerhill%3A%20A%20Photo-Chronicle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28132623%2FDSC_0279.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EObsessed%20as%20I%20have%20been%20with%20my%20camera%20(or%20any%20instrument%20with%20a%20camera%20in%20it)%2C%20there%20were%20other%20things%20I%20just%20began%20to%20freeze%20about%20this%20neighbourhood%20I%20arrived%20in%20only%20in%20January%20this%20year%20and%20in%20a%20different%20mental%20space.%20There%20were%20some%20more%20dramatic%20trees%20and%20creepers%20and%20the%20train%20(6%3A15%20pm%20and%207%3A15%20pm)%20that%20Oli%2C%20my%20canine%20significant%20other%20and%20I%2C%20walked%20past%20every%20morning%20and%20evening%20to%20be%20frozen%2C%20yet%2C%20as%20images%2C%20histories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20late%20for%20the%20walk%20that%20fateful%20morning%20on%20August%2014.%20To%20think%20that%20just%20last%20month%2C%20I%20photographed%20the%20train%20track%20en%20route%20Boileauganj%2C%20and%20a%20few%20Deodars%20with%20character%2C%20and%20Oli%20waiting%20for%20a%20train.%20Today%2C%20that%20path%2C%20and%20train%20track%2C%20are%20out%20of%20access%20for%20ordinary%20people%20like%20us.%20Strange%20it%20seems%20to%20me%20that%20of%20all%20the%20things%2C%20I%20lost%20the%20only%20pictures%20of%20the%20old%20temple%20and%20the%20last%20%3Cem%3Ebhandara%3C%2Fem%3E%20(feast)%20held%20there%20around%20the%20month%20of%20May%2C%20when%20my%20older%20phone%20lost%20its%20life%20in%20in%20a%20freak%20water-related%20accident%20in%20late%20June%20at%20a%20village%20in%20Dharamshala.%20Sometimes%2C%20things%20lost%20in%20a%20gush%20of%20water%20never%20return%2C%20and%20if%20they%20do%2C%20they%20come%20back%20not%20quite%20the%20same%20again%2C%20as%20it%20happened%20here!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20event%20now%20seems%20ominous%20and%20most%20disconcerting%2C%20on%20hindsight.%20The%20only%20image%20that%20I%20now%20have%20is%20of%20the%20smaller%20one%20(with%20meanings%20and%20stories%20that%20people%20share%20everyday)%20built%20by%20Saunkhi%20Ram%20and%20his%20wife%20Shanta%2C%20a%20rare%20structure%20built%20with%20images%20of%20Shiva%2C%20Parvati%20and%20Ganesha%20in%20vernacular%20style%2C%20by%20a%20Dalit%20person%2C%20sitting%20pretty%20with%20the%20older%20structure%2C%20and%20yet%20where%20many%2C%20including%20the%20Pandit%20ji%20(Suman%20Kishore%2C%20who%20died%20in%20the%20disaster)%20offered%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meaning%20of%20life%2C%20it%20appears%2C%20is%20not%20to%20let%20go%20of%20the%20present%20moment%20that%20may%20or%20may%20not%20be%20perfect%20for%20an%20image%2C%20or%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20to%20simply%20let%20go%20of%20an%20image%20that%20was%20never%20meant%20to%20be%20frozen.%20Permanence%20is%20an%20illusion%20and%20one%20feels%20it%20every%20night%20when%20the%20sky%20rumbles%2C%20the%20lightning%20strikes%20and%20the%20downpour%20starts%2C%20and%20the%20earth%20seems%20to%20shift%20a%20bit%20uneasily%20underneath%2C%20perhaps%20in%20her%20longer%20geological%20journey%20that%20we%20have%20no%20idea%20about.%20Who%20would%20have%20believed%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20that%20Prospect%20Hill%2C%20not%20far%20from%20here%2C%20is%20sitting%20on%20a%20volcano%2C%20or%20that%20Shimla%20sat%20on%20a%20sea%20on%20whose%20surface%20icebergs%20once%20floated!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20much%20longer%20history%20that%20we%20seem%20to%20have%20no%20control%20over%2C%20yet%20in%20the%20shorter%20span%20of%20ephemeral%20lives%2C%20we%20come%20to%20believe%20we%20can%20make%20plains%20out%20of%20mountains%20and%20reach%20the%20moon%E2%80%A6%20Yet%2C%20yet%2C%20it%20took%20all%20of%2011%20days%20to%20retrieve%20just%2020%20bodies%20(none%20alive)%20within%20a%20small%20radius%20of%203-4%20km%20for%20an%20army%20of%20men%20from%20the%20SDRF%2C%20NDRF%2C%20police%20personnel%20and%20several%20local%20people%20from%20in%20and%20around%20Summerhill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20questions%20arose%20in%20my%20head%20as%20I%20ran%20up%20and%20downhill%20with%20different%20groups%20of%20search%20teams%20all%20of%20the%20past%2011%20days%2C%20starting%20around%2010%20am%20and%20reaching%20home%20around%206%20pm%2C%20some%20of%20which%20remain%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoes%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98natural%20calamity%E2%80%99%20not%20take%20away%20the%20issue%20from%20human%20responsibility%20and%20over-interference%20in%20the%20natural%20world%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20to%20say%20of%20the%20length%20of%20time%20that%20the%20ground%20in%20the%20IIAS%20was%20sinking%20or%20under%20repair%2C%20or%20whether%20the%20large%20fissures%20on%20the%20path%20through%20the%20forest%20in%20the%20premises%20have%20been%20happening%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%2C%20unnoticed%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20does%20a%20tourist%20obsess%20about%20reaching%20Manali%20or%20Shimla%20from%20Chandigarh%20in%20a%20jiffy%20for%20a%20holiday%3F%20Why%20does%20fast-tracking%20a%20road%20journey%20matter%20so%20much%3F%20What%20necessitated%20the%20four-lanes%20for%20a%20small%20hilly%20region%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHave%20the%20four-lane%20highway%20projects%20started%20the%20process%20of%20slow%20death%20of%20the%20precious%20mountains%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhere%20are%20the%20true%20cracks%20on%20the%20earth%E2%80%99s%20surface%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20ripple%20effect%20impacting%20entire%20Himachal%20so%20badly%3F%20Is%20excessive%20rainfall%20and%20%E2%80%98cloud%20burst%E2%80%99%20the%20only%20geological%2Fmeteorological%20explanation%20left%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20to%20say%20of%20the%20drilling%20(as%20popular%20opinion%20now%20makes%20itself%20audible%20and%20visible%2C%20after%20the%20tragedy%2C%20unfortunately)%20of%20the%20rockface%20behind%20the%20temple%20for%20building%20a%20new%2C%20taller%20Hanuman%20temple%20next%20to%20the%20Shiva%20temple%3F%20Can%20small%2C%20unassuming%20shrines%20of%20faith%20remain%20small%20and%20unassuming%2C%20or%20does%20everything%20have%20to%20be%20larger%20than%20life%3F%20Is%20there%20any%20role%20of%20the%20new%20construction%20on%20the%20space%20in%20the%20matter%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20didn%E2%80%99t%20the%20new%20temple%20contractor%20(many%20local%20stories%20abound)%20pay%20a%20visit%20even%20to%20offer%20condolences%20to%20the%20families%20bereaved%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20the%20Union%20government%20(reported%20in%20the%20media)%20proposing%20to%20construct%20a%20massive%20international%20sports%20complex%20near%20the%20Indrunag%20temple%20near%20Dharamshala%2C%20considering%20its%20fragile%20ecosystem%20and%20the%20massive%20deforestation%20that%20will%20ensue%20in%20a%20prone%20to%20flash-flood%20area%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20government%20commence%20an%20audit%20of%20the%20constructions%20that%20came%20up%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%20(even%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20when%20many%20new%20buildings%20sprouted%20up%3F)%20and%20an%20audit%20of%20the%20older%20buildings%20that%20were%20unsafe%20allowed%20to%20exist%2C%20with%20residents%20living%20in%20them%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20there%20be%20a%20comprehensive%20inquiry%20into%20the%20nature%20of%20spending%20on%20restoration%20works%20in%20IIAS%20premises%2C%20which%20houses%20only%20a%20few%20fellows%20but%20a%20larger%20number%20of%20(more%20importantly)%20staff%20(contractual%20and%20regular)%20across%20designations%20within%20the%20premises%3F%20How%20important%20is%20the%20institutional%20working%20class%20for%20government%20institutions%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20the%20entire%20city%20of%20Shimla%20in%20grave%20danger%2C%20considering%20the%20collapse%20of%20few%20structures%20and%20declaration%20of%20few%20others%20as%20unsafe%2C%20even%20as%20roads%20have%20been%20caving%20in%20at%20several%20locations%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20didn%E2%80%99t%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20railway%20minister%20pay%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20disaster%20sites%2C%20which%20included%20the%20heritage%20structures%20of%20IIAS%20and%20the%20UNESCO%20heritage%20Shimla-Kalka%20rail%20line%2C%20when%20otherwise%20you%20saw%20them%20feverishly%20inaugurating%20every%20Vande%20Bharat%20express%20everywhere%20else%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20didn%E2%80%99t%20the%20director%20of%20IIAS%20feel%20it%20necessary%20to%20pay%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20disaster%20site%20in%20a%20suburb%20not%20far%20from%20the%20institute%2C%20even%20if%20to%20offer%20condolences%20to%20the%20families%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20some%20questions%20for%20all%20(apology%20Dylan)%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20many%20years%20can%20a%20mountain%20exist%2C%20before%20it%E2%80%99s%20washed%20%5Bin%20the%20greed%20of%20the%20political%20class%2C%20the%20contractors%2C%20and%20the%20consumption-tourists%5D%20to%20the%20sea%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20many%20deaths%20will%20it%20take%20till%20%5Bwe%5D%20know%2C%20that%20too%20many%20people%20have%20died%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20answer%E2%80%A6is%20blowin%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%E2%80%A6%20across%20rivers%20and%20clouds%20and%20mountains%20and%20the%20earth%20beneath%20our%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20long%20will%20it%20take%20for%20us%20to%20hear%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20it%2C%20I%20let%20the%20images%20tell%20their%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERelief%20efforts%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28132610%2FDSC_0278.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28132610%2FDSC_0278.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28132610%2FDSC_0278-