0that%20all%20those%20Muslim%20children%20should%20be%E2%80%A6(inaudible)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%2040-second-long%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fup-pressure-on-boys-family-to-compromise-in-slapping-incident-as-politicians-swarm-the-village%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20has%20been%20pressure%20on%20the%20young%20boy%E2%80%99s%20family%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccompromise%E2%80%9D%20and%20not%20take%20charges%20against%20the%20teacher%20forward.%20Tyagi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fslapping-muzaffarnagar-school-student-muslim-tripti-tyagi%5C%22%3Ehas%20claimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20did%20nothing%20wrong%20and%20there%20was%20nothing%20communal%20about%20her%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZubair%20was%20arrested%20and%20put%20in%20jail%20for%20three%20weeks%20in%20June-July%202022%2C%20and%20multiple%20cases%20filed%20against%20him%20for%20a%20tweet%20in%20which%20he%20had%20shared%20a%20screenshot%20from%20an%20old%20Bollywood%20film.%20He%20was%20released%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693212349000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F30134445%2FScreenshot-2022-07-30-at-1.44.32-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fvendetta-up-police-files-fir-against-alt-news-journalist-for-tweet-on-muslim-boy-slapped%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohammed%20Zubair%20told%20The%20Wire%20that%20an%20FIR%20had%20been%20lodged%20against%20him%20even%20though%20he%20had%20later%20deleted%20the%20video%20and%20notified%20his%20followers%20on%20social%20media%20site%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fvendetta-up-police-files-fir-against-alt-news-journalist-for-tweet-on-muslim-boy-slapped%22%2C%2