s%20tough%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20appealed%20for%20anyone%20with%20information%20or%20digital%20footage%20of%20the%20attack%20to%20come%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693209780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fddvce4e8_aurman-singh_625x300_28_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faurman-singh-4-indian-origin-men-charged-for-murdering-23-year-old-delivery-agent-in-uk-4335491%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20Indian-origin%20men%20in%20their%2020s%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20the%20murder%20of%20a%2023-year-old%20delivery%20driver%2C%20also%20of%20Indian%20heritage%2C%20after%20an%20attack%20in%20Shrewsbury%2C%20western%20England.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faurman-singh-4-indian-origin-men-charged-for-murdering-23-year-old-delivery-agent-in-uk-4335491%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20Bags%20Worlds%20Gold%2C%20Arshad%20Makes%20Big%20Olympics%20Prediction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECompeting%20with%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics%20Gold%20medal%20winner%2C%20Pakistan's%20Arshad%20Nadeem%20bagged%20the%20second%20spot%20on%20the%20podium%20at%20the%20World%20Athletics%20Championships%20in%20the%20Javelin%20Throw%20final.%20It%20was%20Neeraj%20who%20once%20again%20bagged%20the%20top%20spot%2C%20earning%20his%20maiden%20World%20Championships%20gold.%20But%2C%20in%20a%20sport%20that%20has%20traditionally%20been%20dominated%20by%20European%20countries%2C%20the%20top%20two%20spots%20went%20to%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20--%20two%20Asian%20countries.%20As%20the%20focus%20now%20shifts%20to%20the%20Asian%20Games%20and%20the%202024%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20Pakistan's%20Arshad%20feels%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20will%20once%20again%20finish%201-2%20in%20next%20year's%20quadrennial