sehold%20items%20have%20been%20left%20intact.%20Even%20the%20%3Cem%3Epucca%3C%2Fem%3E%20roofs%20were%20broken%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-dalit-man-killed-mother-stripped-over-daughters-sex-assault-complaint-4334923%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20violence%20at%20their%20house%2C%20the%20mob%20went%20looking%20for%20the%20woman%E2%80%99s%20two%20other%20sons.%20The%20victim%E2%80%99s%20aunt%20said%20a%20mob%20barged%20into%20her%20house%20too%20and%20threatened%20her%20family.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20would%20have%20killed%20my%20children%20and%20husband%20too.%20They%20even%20checked%20our%20fridge%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20situation%20remains%20tense%20in%20the%20village%20with%20heavy%20police%20force%20deployed%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20family%20performed%20his%20final%20rites%20after%20the%20district%20collector%20assured%20them%20of%20help%20under%20government%20schemes%20and%20informed%20them%20of%20the%20arrests%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20sister%20had%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20four%20men%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20threatening%20and%20beating%20her.%20All%20four%20were%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20that%20is%20now%20in%20the%20courts%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fhow-the-savarna-makers-of-made-in-heaven-failed-to-build-ethical-collaboration%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20Savarna%20Makers%20of%20%E2%80%98Made%20in%20Heaven%E2%80%99%20Failed%20to%20Build%20Ethical%20Collaboration%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20triggered%20a%20political%20row%20in%20election-bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20with%20the%20opposition%20parties%2C%20Congress%20and%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20slamming%20the%20Bharatiya%