9557%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ffrance-bans-muslim-students-from-wearing-abaya-dress-in-state-schools-12949557%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRetribution%3F%26quot%3B%3A%20Court%20Asks%20Why%20Lecturer%20Suspended%20After%20Article%20370%20Hearing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20directed%20the%20centre's%20top%20law%20officer%20to%20speak%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20and%20find%20out%20why%20a%20lecturer%20in%20the%20union%20territory's%20Education%20Department%20was%20suspended%20days%20after%20he%20appeared%20in%20court%20to%20argue%20against%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370.%20The%20court%20wanted%20to%20know%20if%20the%20suspension%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20lecturer's%20appearance%20before%20the%20court%20and%20indicated%20it%20would%20take%20a%20dim%20view%20if%20this%20was%20the%20case%2C%20suggesting%20it%20might%20be%20seen%20as%20%26quot%3Bretribution%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20last%20week%2C%20Zahoor%20Ahmad%20Bhat%20-%20a%20senior%20political%20science%20lecturer%20with%20a%20law%20degree%20-%20appeared%20before%20a%20five-judge%20Constitution%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20later%2C%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Education%20Department%20issued%20an%20order%20suspending%20Mr%20Bhat%2C%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20for%20violating%20provisions%20of%20the%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20Civil%20Service%20Regulations%2C%20the%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20Government%20Employees%20Conduct%20Rules%20and%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Leave%20Rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%2C%20issued%20by%20the%20Education%20Department's%20Principal%20Secretary%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20period%20of%20suspension%2C%20delinquent%20shall%20remain%20attached%20in%20the%20office%20of%20Directorate%20of%20School%20Educa