hi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Four%20men%20from%20the%20Dalit%20community%20were%20hung%20upside%20down%20from%20a%20tree%20and%20assaulted%20by%20six%20persons%20in%20Ahmednagar%20district%20of%20Maharashtra%20on%20August%2025.%20The%20men%2C%20all%20in%20their%2020s%2C%20were%20accused%20by%20the%20mob%20of%20stealing%20some%20livestock%2C%20according%20to%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20video%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20which%20took%20place%20in%20Haregaon%20village%20of%20Shrirampur%20taluka%2C%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media%2C%20the%20police%20arrested%20one%20person%20on%20August%2026%2C%20while%20five%20others%20are%20absconding%2C%20an%20officer%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2F4-dalit-men-hung-upside-down-from-tree-beaten-up-in-maharashtra-over-suspicion-of-theft%2Farticle67242390.ece%5C%22%3Ethe%20news%20agency%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20six%20persons%20from%20the%20village%20%E2%80%93%20identified%20as%20Yuvraj%20Galande%2C%20Manoj%20Bodake%2C%20Pappu%20Parkhe%2C%20Deepak%20Gaikwad%2C%20Durgesh%20Vaidya%20and%20Raju%20Borage%20%E2%80%93%20allegedly%20picked%20up%20the%20four%20Dalit%20men%20from%20their%20homes%20and%20tied%20them%20up%20to%20a%20tree%20upside%20down%20and%20beat%20them%20with%20sticks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20under%20Sections%20307%20(attempt%20to%20murder)%2C%20364%20(kidnapping)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20and%20some%20sections%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20shutdown%20was%20observed%20in%20Haregaon%20village%20on%20August%2027%20to%20protest%20the%20incident%2C%20according%20to%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20Congress%20and%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20have%20condemned%20the%20attack.%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20president%20Nana%20Patole%20said%20the%20incident%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cblot%20on%20humanity%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%2