d%20to%20coordinate%20with%20the%20Indian%20army%20and%20other%20central%20security%20forces%20to%20start%20transporting%20essential%20commodities%20to%20the%20hill%20district%20of%20Churachandpur%20from%20August%2028%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmanipur-tribal-district-to-get-essentials-via-alternative-routes%2Farticle67241952.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20The%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Manipur%20government%20official%20told%20the%20paper%20that%20it%20is%20ensuring%20that%20medical%20supplies%20reach%20the%20district%20through%20aerial%20routes%20and%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%2C%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20Manipur%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20measures%20have%20been%20taken%20because%20the%20government%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20open%20the%20land%20routes%20within%20the%20strife-torn%20state.%20Ethnic%20violence%20has%20roiled%20Manipur%20since%20May%203%2C%20killing%20upwards%20of%20150%20people%20and%20displacing%20tens%20of%20thousands.%20The%20state%20is%20now%20divided%20into%20territories%20controlled%20by%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20moment%2C%20blockades%20are%20on%20at%20the%20National%20Highway%20that%20connects%20Dimapur%20and%20Imphal%2C%20and%20on%20the%20Churachandpur%20Road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20began%20on%20August%2021%2C%20and%20was%20called%20by%20the%20Committee%20on%20Tribal%20Unity%20(COTU)%20at%20Kangpokpi.%20This%20has%20affected%20the%20supply%20of%20essentials%20to%20Meitei%20dominated%20places.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20critical%20situation%20as%20an%20alternative%20route%20exists%20to%20supply%20the%20valley%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccess%20to%20Churachandpur%20is%20blocked%20by%20women-led%20Meitei%20groups%20and%20transporters%20have%20refused%20to%20ply%20on%20their%20routes%20citing%20personal%20safety%2C%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20so%20far%20also%20failed%20to%20give%20access%20to%20the%20airport%20at%20Imphal%20to%20the%20hill%20residents%2C%20particularly%20to%20the%20Kuki%20community.%20Those%20located%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district%20have%20to%20wheel%20down%20to%20neighbouring%20Nagaland%20to%20board%20a%20flight%20from%20Dimapur%20airport.%20The%20Kukis%20from%20the%20Churachandpur%20area%20have%20been%20taking%20the%20day-long%20road%20route%20to%20Aizawl%20in%20Mizoram%20for%20air%20connectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthree-months-later-has-amit-shah-fulfilled-the-promises-he-made-on-manipur%5C%22%3Ereported%20earlier%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20helicopter%20service%20to%20the%20Imphal%20airport%20from%20the%20hill%20areas%20has%20not%20taken%20off%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20in%20depth%20how%20one%20of%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20promises%20to%20Manipur%2C%20during%20his%20visit%2C%20was%20that%20eight%20medical%20teams%20would%20be%20sent%20there.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20teams%20will%20provide%20health%20facilities%20in%20Moreh%2C%20Churachandpur%20and%20Kangpokpi%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20found%20that%2035%20people%20have%20already%20died%20in%20Churachandpur%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20medicines%20and%20proper%20treatment%20at%20the%20hospital%20in%20the%20district%2C%20according%20to%20Kuki%20Khanglai%20Lawmpi%2C%20a%20Kuki%20civil%20society%20organisation%20that%20has%20been%20providing%20medical%20aid%20in%20relief%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt%20that%20at%20the%20time%20of%20publishing%20the%20report%2C%20there%20is%20a%20shortage%20of%20medicines%20in%20Saparmeina%20village%20in%20Kangpokpi%2C%20and%20that%20six%20people%20are%20in%20immediate%20need%20of%20medical%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20demand%20for%20separate%20administration%20has%20been%20raised%20by%20the%20Kuki%20community%20due%20to%20the%20May%203%20violence%2C%20powerful%20Meitei%20civil%20society%20organisations%20like%20COCOMI%20have%20been%20holding%20rallies%20in%20the%20valley%20areas%20with%20the%20counter%20demand%20that%20the%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20Manipur%20must%20be%20maintained.%20However%2C%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20latest%20measures%20to%20reach%20one%20large%20part%20of%20the%20state%20aerially%20only%20indicates%20its%20inability%20to%20surmount%20the%20territorial%20divide%20created%20post%20May%203%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693203165000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F15203438%2FSurgical-ward-at-Churachandpur-hospital-II.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchurachandpur-blockade-air-route-essential-manipur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20measures%20have%20been%20taken%20because%20the%20government%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20open%20the%20land%20routes%20within%20the%20strife-torn%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchurachandpur-blockade-air-route-essential-manipur%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aamir%20hosts%20a%20get-together%20for%20LSC%20team%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693203064000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103124094%2Cimgsize-48294.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Faamir-khan-hosts-a-get-together-for-team-laal-singh-chaddha-report%2Farticleshow%2F103124094.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103124094.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAamir%20Khan%20reportedly%20hosted%20a%20get-together%20party%20for%20the%20team%20of%20'Laal%20Singh%20Chaddha'%20to%20celebrate%20the%20film's%20success%20on%20OTT%20platforms.%20Naga%20Chaitanya%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20film%2C%20praised%20Aamir's%20work%20ethic%20and%20said%20he%20sees%20working%20on%20the%20project%20as%20an%20investment%20for%20the%20future.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Faamir-khan-hosts-a-get-together-for-team-laal-singh-chaddha-report%2Farticleshow%2F103124094.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anger%20Brews%20in%20Jammu%20as%20Traders%2C%20Locals%20Accuse%20the%20BJP%20of%20Misgovernance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120115%2FJammu-bandh-pic-01.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CKashmiris%20were%20100%25%20better%20than%20you%20(Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party).%20We%20were%20happy%20with%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370.We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20that%20they%20are%20destroying%20us.%20Article%20370%20was%20our%20identity%20and%20safety.%20We%20are%20Dogras!%20Kashmiris%20were%20also%20scared%20of%20us.%20We%20would%20boast%20of%20our%20Dogra%20identity.%20If%20they%20(Kashmiri%20politicians)%20would%20get%20Rs%2020%2C%20they%20would%20give%20us%20Rs%2010.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20utterances%20of%20the%20father%20of%20the%20president%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Yuva%20Rajput%20Sabha%2C%20an%20organisation%20spearheading%20protests%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region%20to%20seek%20suspension%20of%20a%20toll%20plaza%20in%20Sarore%20Samba%2C%20shows%20how%20the%20thinking%20of%20people%20in%20Jammu%20has%20changed%20over%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government.%20The%20video%20in%20which%20he%20makes%20these%20remarks%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20over%20the%20toll%20plaza%20have%20become%20a%20platform%20for%20Jammuities%20to%20vent%20their%20anger%20over%20a%20series%20of%20moves%20by%20the%20union%20territory%E2%80%99s%20unelected%20government%20after%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20reorganisation%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%20August%202019.%20The%20region%20observed%20a%20complete%20shutdown%20on%20August%2026%20(Saturday)%20and%20witnessed%20protests%20and%20slogans%20against%20the%20union%20territory%E2%80%99s%20administration%20and%20the%20BJP.%20The%20protests%20in%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20citadel%20over%20governance%20issues%20fly%20in%20the%20face%20of%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20LG-led%20administration%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20on%20the%20path%20of%20progress%20and%20development%20after%20the%20constitutional%20changes%20of%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20the%20protests%20begin%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20began%20with%20the%20Yuva%20Rajput%20Sabha%20(YRS)%20issuing%20an%20ultimatum%20to%20the%20administration%20to%20suspend%20toll%20collection%20at%20Sarore%20Plaza%20due%20to%20the%20bad%20condition%20of%20the%20road%20and%20damage%20to%20a%20bridge%20at%20Dayalachak%20on%20the%20Jammu-Pathankot%20highway.%20On%20August%2021%2C%20YRS%20held%20a%20protest%20rally%20near%20the%20toll%20plaza.%20Some%20people%20also%20pelted%20stones%20at%20the%20plaza%20and%20damaged%20glass%20windows%2C%20prompting%20the%20administration%20to%20impose%20Section%20144%20around%20the%20toll%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20at%20night%20on%20August%2021%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20police%20arrested%2026%20leaders%20from%20the%20Sarore%20toll%20post%2C%20sparking%20off%20massive%20protests%20in%20the%20region.%20Soon%2C%20opposition%20political%20parties%20joined%20in%20and%20held%20protests%20against%20the%20administration.%20On%20August%2026%2C%20the%20region%20witnessed%20a%20complete%20%3Cem%3Ebandh%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20call%20of%20the%20Jammu%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industries%20against%20the%20Sarore%20toll%20plaza%20and%20installation%20of%20smart%20electric%20metres.%20The%20protesters%20mocked%20the%20BJP%20with%20slogans%20of%20%E2%80%9CJammu%2C%20Jammu%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20a%20slogan%20often%20raised%20by%20BJP%20leader%20Devinder%20Rana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120155%2FJammu-bandh-pic-06.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120155%2FJammu-bandh-pic-06.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120155%2FJammu-bandh-pic-06-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120155%2FJammu-bandh-pic-06-1024x686.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670162%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22804%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Jammu%20bandh%20on%20Saturday.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20or%20its%20earlier%20avatar%20Jan%20Sangh%2C%20has%20been%20projecting%20itself%20as%20a%20protector%20of%20the%20interests%20of%20Jammu.%20The%20right-wing%20party%20has%20often%20accused%20successive%20regimes%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20of%20poor%20treatment%20towards%20the%20region%20and%20bias%20in%20favour%20of%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state%2C%20it%20had%20objected%20to%20setting%20up%20a%20toll%20plaza%20at%20Lakhanpur%20and%20compared%20it%20to%20the%20collection%20of%20%3Cem%3Ejaziya%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0from%20Vaishno%20Devi%20pilgrims%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Katra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20workers%2C%20led%20by%20Chandra%20Prakash%20Ganga%20who%20became%20minister%20in%20the%20PDP-BJP%20coalition%20government%20in%202015%2C%20dismantled%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20Sarore%20toll%20plaza%20in%20May%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJammu%20fumes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20fourth%20time%20after%20August%205%2C%202019%20that%20Jammu%20has%20observed%20a%20shutdown%20over%20economic%20issues.%20It%20observed%20bandhs%20on%20the%20imposition%20of%20property%20tax%2C%20proposal%20of%20opening%20of%20Reliance%20retail%20stores%2C%20and%20lawyers%E2%80%99%20demand%20for%20housing%20quasi-judicial%20bodies%20and%20the%20Central%20Administrative%20Tribunal%20(CAT)%20at%20one%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJammu%20has%20been%20betrayed%20and%20backstabbed%2C%E2%80%9D%20advocate%20Sheikh%20Shakeel%20Ahmad%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Jammu%20was%20promised%20that%20its%20lands%20and%20jobs%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20compromised%2C%20but%20there%20are%20no%20safeguards%20for%20the%20region%20like%20Ladakh.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20major%20contracts%20have%20gone%20to%20outsiders.%20The%20outsiders%20have%20taken%20away%20major%20contracts%20in%20mining%20and%20others%20business%20avenues%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20abolishing%20of%20the%20practice%20of%20the%20administration%E2%80%99s%20darbar%20move%20(moving%20the%20winter%20capital%20from%20Srinagar%20to%20Jammu)%20has%20crippled%20business%20in%20Jammu.%20%E2%80%9CLakhs%20of%20Kashmiris%20would%20visit%20Jammu%20in%20winters%20and%20spend%20crores%20of%20rupees%20here.%20Now%20less%20people%20visit%20the%20region%20after%20the%20government%20abolished%20the%20darbar%20move%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20darbar%20move%20was%20a%20149-year-old%20official%20practice%20of%20rotating%20the%20seat%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20governance%20between%20the%20twin%20capitals%20of%20Srinagar%20and%20Jammu%20on%20a%20bi-annual%20basis.%20It%20was%20abolished%20in%202021%20by%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20led%20by%20Manoj%20Sinha%2C%20saying%20it%20will%20save%20the%20state%20exchequer%20Rs%20200%20crore%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArun%20Gupta%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Jammu%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industries%20(JCCI)%2C%20said%20that%20there%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20disturb%20the%20business%20community%20of%20Jammu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20them%20(government)%20keep%20their%20focus%20on%20Kashmir%2C%20but%20they%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20don%E2%80%99t%20disturb%20us.%20We%20are%20not%20anti-nationals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120259%2FJammu-bandh-pic-04.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120259%2FJammu-bandh-pic-04.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120259%2FJammu-bandh-pic-04-300x197.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28120259%2FJammu-bandh-pic-04-1024x671.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670164%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22786%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Jammu%20bandh%20on%20Saturday.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Jammu%20bandh%20was%20a%20historic%20shutdown%20and%20the%20government%20should%20talk%20to%20the%20people%20to%20understand%20their%20grievances.%20%E2%80%9CAbolition%20of%20the%20darbar%20move%20practice%20has%20not%20only%20affected%20business%20in%20the%20region%2C%20but%20it%20has%20also%20potential%20to%20create%20differences%20between%20two%20regions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jammu%20region%20also%20witnessed%20massive%20protests%20by%20unemployed%20youth%20in%20May%20this%20year%20over%20engagement%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cblacklisted%E2%80%9D%20company%20by%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Service%20Selection%20Board%20(SSB)%20for%20conducting%20job%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20on%20sticky%20wicket%2C%20Kashmir%20%26amp%3B%20Jammu%20come%20closer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20finds%20itself%20in%20a%20tight%20spot%20over%20the%20situation%20unfolding%20in%20Jammu%2C%20the%20political%20and%20psychological%20divergences%20between%20Kashmir%20and%20Jammu%20are%20narrowing%20down%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20local%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20distance%20itself%20from%20decisions%20of%20the%20UT%E2%80%99s%20administration.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20is%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20any%20forcible%20taxation%20or%20demolition.%20This%20tax%20(property)%20has%20not%20been%20imposed%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20the%20LG%E2%80%99s%20administration.%20However%2C%20paying%20a%20trivial%20amount%20of%20tax%20would%20ensure%20crores%20of%20funds%20for%20development%20of%20civic%20amenities%20like%20roads%2C%20electricity%2C%20lanes%2C%20water%20and%20drains%2C%E2%80%9D%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20J%26amp%3BK%20president%20Ravinder%20Raina%20told%20mediapersons%20in%20February%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Jammu%E2%80%99s%20Dogri-speaking%20areas%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20a%20power%20tussle%20from%20Praja%20Parishad%20days%2C%20are%20becoming%20psychologically%