ittle%20use%20while%20imagining%20someone%E2%80%99s%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20wish%20we%20knew%20what%20it%20was%20to%20be%2C%20against%20dying%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3Eto%20know%20the%20dignity%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3Ethat%20had%20to%20be%20earned%20dangerously%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3Eyour%20last%20chance%20that%20was%20blindly%20terrifying%2C%20so%20unfair.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPain%20was%20not%20Mahapatra%E2%80%99s%20prison.%20It%20also%20expanded%20his%20consciousness%20and%20gave%20him%20the%20capacity%20for%20hope.%20It%20made%20him%20sensitive%20to%20the%20pain%20of%20others.%20From%20the%20terrified%20bleating%20of%20goats%20being%20led%20to%20the%20slaughterhouse%20to%20the%20cries%20of%20a%20newly%20wed%20girl%20as%20she%20was%20burnt%20by%20her%20in-laws%2C%20from%20the%20loss%20of%20his%20wife%2C%20his%20only%20son%2C%20and%20his%20beloved%20caretaker%20to%20a%20lifetime%20of%20severe%20migraines%20and%20asthma%2C%20Mahapatra%20kept%20discovering%20and%20distilling%20the%20sombre%20lyricism%20in%20pathos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22tl%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EJayanta%20Mahapatra%3Cbr%3E(22%20October%201928%20%E2%80%93%2027%20August%202023)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRsFHLmcz3n%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FRsFHLmcz3n%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Ronald%20Tuhin%20D'Rozario%20(%40rtdrozario)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frtdrozario%2Fstatus%2F1695966547976876252%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2028%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20pain%20can%20also%20numb%20the%20senses%20to%20an%20extent%2C%20becoming%20its%20own%20analgesic.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20a%20life%20singed%20with%20painful%20memories%20can%20also%20find%20pleasure%20in%20discomfort.%20Once%2C%20Mahapatra%20was%20asked%20why%20he%20chose%20to%20spend%20his%20life%20in%20Cuttack%20town%20rather%20than%20settle%20anywhere%20else%2C%20especially%20when%20he%20had%20opportunities%20to%20establish%20a%20good%20life%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20see%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20had%20said%20with%20a%20mischievous%20smile%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20rather%20fond%20of%20the%20smelly%2C%20open%20drains%20of%20Cuttack%20town.%20My%20liking%20for%20stench%20and%20sludge%20must%20have%20something%20to%20do%20with%20all%20the%20dirt%20my%20mother%20said%20I%20used%20to%20eat%20as%20a%20child.%20But%20to%20me%2C%20it%20was%20a%20taste%20of%20the%20sweet%20soil%20of%20my%20beloved%20Cuttack%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESampad%20Patnaik%20is%20a%20freelance%20journalist%20based%20in%20Odisha.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693202195000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28082709%2FUntitled-design-1-4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fpoet-jayanta-mahapatra-passes-away-obituary%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Considered%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20Indian%20poets%20in%20the%20English%20language%2C%20Mahapatra%20passed%20away%20in%20his%20hometown%20of%20Cuttack%20in%20Odisha%20at%20the%20age%20of%2095.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A52%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fpoet-jayanta-mahapatra-passes-away-obituary%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hannah%20Montana%20star%20charged%20with%20theft%20and%20public%20intoxication%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693201380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-miley-cyrus-mitchel-musso_6265547.jpg%3F20230828065639%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhannah-montana-star-mitchel-musso-charged-with-theft-and-public-intoxication-12949510%22%2C%22su