22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDA%20Like%20an%20Amoeba%2C%20Has%20No%20Clear%20Shape%20or%20Size%3A%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28102306%2FUddhav-Thackeray.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EFormer%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20head%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20on%20Sunday%20(August%2027)%20said%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20is%20like%20an%20%E2%80%9Camoeba%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20as%20it%20lack%20a%20definite%20shape%20and%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThackeray%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flike-amoeba-nda-has-no-definite-shape-and-size-uddhav-thackeray-4334109%5C%22%3Eremarks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20made%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Hingoli%2C%20came%20days%20before%20the%20planned%20INDIA%20(opposition%20alliance)%20meet%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20August%2030%20and%20September%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20INDIA%20alliance%20comprises%20nationalist%20parties%20that%20want%20to%20protect%20democracy%20in%20the%20country.%20But%20most%20parties%20in%20the%20NDA%20comprise%20traitors%20and%20those%20who%20have%20joined%20the%20BJP%20as%20allies%20by%20breaking%20other%20parties%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thackeray%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20present%20NDA%20is%20like%20an%20amoeba%2C%20which%20has%20no%20definite%20shape%20and%20size%E2%80%A6The%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20hit%20out%20at%20BJP%20leaders%20who%20have%20said%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20should%20be%20called%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eghamandiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(arrogant)%E2%80%99%20saying%20the%20NDA%20could%20easily%20be%20called%20%E2%80%98ghama-NDA%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20touched%20down%20on%20the%20Moon%E2%80%A6the%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20in%20South%20Africa%E2%80%A6he%20was%20waving%20the%20national%20flag%E2%80%A6who%20was%20he%20representing%E2%80%A6India%20or%20Indian%20Mujahideen%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thackeray%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fmaharashtra%2Fwhat-if-we-call-nda-as-ghamandiya-uddhav-hits-out-at-bjp-ahead-of-india-meet-2662769%5C%22%3Ealso%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fuddhav-thackeray-warns-against-communal-tension-says-bjp-can-do-anything-to-divert-attention-from-its-governments-failures%2Fcid%2F1961990%5C%22%3Eaccused%20the%20BJP%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20being%20willing%20to%20stoop%20to%20any%20levels%20necessary%20to%20win%20an%20election%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20saying%20this%2C%20former%20governor%20Satyapal%20Malik%2C%20who%20was%20close%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20and%20Trinamul%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20have%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20can%20do%20anything%20to%20win%20the%202024%20election.%20They%20have%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20Pulwama%20incident%20in%202019%20and%20have%20expressed%20fears%20that%20communal%20riots%20can%20be%20triggered%20on%20a%20massive%20scale%20after%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shive%20Sena%20leader%20also%20asked%20why%20the%20BJP%20was%20hosting%20an%20India-Pakistan%20cricket%20match%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20stadium%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20when%20Pakistan%20%E2%80%9Cfunds%20terrorism%E2%80%9D%20and%20has%20refused%20to%20release%20Kulbhushan%20Jadhav.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20World%20Cup%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20match%20will%20be%20held%20in%C2%A0Ahmedabad.%20If%20you%20compare%20our%20India%20alliance%20with%20Indian%20Mujahideen(IM)%20then%20tell%20me%20how%20are%20you%20holding%20a%20cricket%20Match%20with%20Pakistan%20which%20supports%20IM%20and%20terrorists.%20You%20teach%20us%20lessons%20of%20patriotism%20and%20then%20hold%20an%20India-Pakistan%20cricket%20match%20in%C2%A0Ahmedabad.%20Is%20this%20your%20Hindutva%3F%C2%A0Sushma%20Swaraj%20was%20better%20than%20you%2C%20she%20clearly%20stated%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20cricket%20until%20the%20terror%20activities%20against%20India%20are%20not%20stopped%2C%20by%20Pakistan.%20This%20is%20called%20patriotism.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20you%20are%20teaching%20us%20patriotism%20and%20then%20hugging%20those(enemies)%20this%20is%20not%20Hindutva.%20Modi%20ji%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20suit%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fuddhav-thackeray-bjp-india-pak-wc-match-modi-stadium-8912006%2F%5C%22%3EThackeray%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Jadhav%2C%20the%20leader%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%9CNow%20you%20are%20playing%20cricket%20with%20Pakistan.%20The%20match%20will%20be%20held%20at%C2%A0Narendra%20Modi%C2%A0Stadium%20in%C2%A0Ahmedabad.%20Are%20you%20going%20to%20invite%C2%A0Kulbhushan%20Jadhav%20for%20that%20match%3F%20He%20is%20rotting%20in%20a%20Pakistani%20jail.%20Modi%20ji%20what%20are%20you%20doing%20for%20the%20release%20of%20Kulbhushan%20Jadhav%3F%20He%20was%20caught%20while%20working%20for%20our%20country.%20When%20Sushama%20Swaraj%20was%20there%20we%20had%20hopes%20that%20Kulbhushan%20may%20return%20but%20now%20there%20is%20not%20a%20single%20word%20about%20him.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20whether%20he%20is%20alive%20there%20or%20not%2C%20and%20shamelessly%20we%20are%20playing%20cricket%20with%20Pakistan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThackeray%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Fuddhav-thackeray-slams-outsider-kcr-calls-brs-b-team-of-bjp-in-maharashtra-rally-101693163014915.html%5C%22%3Ehit%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao-led%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%2C%20calling%20it%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20B-team%20out%20to%20divide%20anti-BJP%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693198438000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2