e%20senses%20and%20arouse%20the%20spirit.%20The%20expression%20of%20intense%20sensitivity%20anchored%20in%20the%20pulsating%20vibrance%20of%20rhyming%20words%20enhances%20its%20appeal.%20Its%20lyrical%20pull%20magnifies%20the%20force%20of%20the%20message%20of%20togetherness%2C%20compassion%2C%20justice%20and%20injustice%2C%20love%20and%20hate%2C%20identity%20and%20difference%2C%20submission%20and%20assertion%2C%20anger%20and%20anguish%20et%20al%2C%20in%20a%20symphony%20of%20life%E2%80%99s%20many%20hues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPoetry%20creates%20its%20own%20music%20and%20is%20about%20moments%20in%20life%20with%20which%20it%20is%20entwined.%20It%20assembles%20%E2%80%9Clanguage%20into%20art%E2%80%9D%20freeing%20the%20poet%20to%20be%20both%20%E2%80%9Cdignified%20and%20bold%E2%80%9D.%20It%20%E2%80%9Cfills%20the%20air%2C%20rustles%20the%20leaves%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20poet%20weaves%20the%20truth%20of%20his%20age%20in%20the%20image%20of%20his%20own%20experiences.%20Sahir%20Ludhianvi%E2%80%99s%20introduction%20to%20his%20poetry%20says%20it%20all%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cduniy%C4%81%20ne%20tajrab%C4%81t%20o%20hav%C4%81dis%20k%C4%AB%20shakl%20me%C3%B1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejo%20kuchh%20mujhe%20diy%C4%81%20hai%2C%20vo%20lauT%C4%81%20rah%C4%81%20huu%C3%B1%20main%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%5B%E2%80%9CWhatever%20the%20world%20has%20given%20to%20me%20by%20way%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Eexperience%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20accident%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20what%20I%20am%20returning%E2%80%9D%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20soul%20of%20the%20author%20is%20laid%20bare%20in%20his%20poetry%20%E2%80%93%20a%20%E2%80%98voice%20that%20survives%20the%20silencing%20of%20the%20voice%E2%80%99.%20Inspired%20by%20compelling%20emotions%20and%20sheltered%20in%20the%20depth%20of%20private%20