3Cspan%3E%5B%20Shakeel%2C%20I%20am%20but%20an%20echo%20of%20my%20heart%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20confidante%20of%20the%20emotion%20of%20love%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20proud%2C%20my%20poetry%20and%20life%20are%20not%20apart.%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20their%20wider%20philosophical%20imagination%2C%20the%20litterateurs%20interrogate%20the%20injustices%20of%20the%20times%20%E2%80%98in%20the%20still%20sad%20music%20of%20humanity.%E2%80%99%20Whether%20in%20depicting%20despair%2C%20ecstasy%20of%20the%20pain%20of%20unrequited%20love%2C%20hopelessness%2C%20the%20romanticism%20of%20protest%20or%20heroism%20of%20the%20brave%2C%20all%20have%20found%20immortality%20in%20literature.%20So%20it%20is%20that%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20histories%20of%20the%20Age%20and%20nations%20are%20encased%20in%20their%20literature%20that%20clothes%20the%20bones%20of%20history%20in%20the%20culture%20of%20our%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20uniting%20philosophy%2C%20feeling%20and%20verve%2C%20art%20keeps%20alive%20the%20wisdom%20of%20the%20ages%20that%20shows%20us%20the%20way.%20Bertolt%20Brecht%20reminded%20us%20that%20art%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20a%20mirror%20held%20up%20to%20reality%20but%20a%20hammer%20with%20which%20to%20shape%20it.%E2%80%9D%20Treasured%20compositions%20of%20the%20masters%20that%20encase%20profound%20wisdom%20and%20sensibilities%20of%20their%20time%20in%20the%20sublime%20arrangement%20of%20words%2C%20define%20for%20us%20our%20humanity%2C%20giving%20us%20the%20music%20of%20our%20lives%20and%20the%20light%20that%20brightens%20our%20path.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20literature%20flavours%20and%20deepens%20the%20expression%20of%20intense%20human%20emotions%2C%20particularly%2C%20the%20pain%20of%20loneliness%2C%20ache%20of%20separation%20from%20loved%20ones%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20rejection%20and%20helplessness.%20Jai%20Shankar%20Prasad%E2%80%99s%20celebrated%20poem%20%E2%80%98Ansoo%E2%80%99%2C%20for