3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%5B%E2%80%9CI%20am%20helpless%2C%20as%20are%20you%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Helpless%20is%20this%20whole%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Despair%20weighs%20on%20my%20mind%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0The%20price%20of%20living%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0is%20either%20the%20gallows%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Eor%20wretchedness.%E2%80%9D%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20he%20expresses%20his%20solidarity%20with%20the%20commoners%20and%20commitment%20to%20their%20dignity%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Clekin%20ai%20azmat-e-ins%C4%81%C3%B1%20ke%20sunahre%20%E1%B8%B3hv%C4%81bo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emai%C3%B1%20kis%C4%AB%20taaj%20k%C4%AB%20satvat%20k%C4%81%20parast%C4%81r%20nah%C4%AB%C3%B1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emere%20afk%C4%81r%20k%C4%81%20unv%C4%81n-e-ir%C4%81dat%20tum%20ho%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emai%C3%B1%20tumh%C4%81r%C4%81%20huu%C3%B1%20luTero%C3%B1%20k%C4%81%20vaf%C4%81d%C4%81r%20nah%C4%AB%C3%B1%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%5B%E2%80%9CBut%20O%20golden%20dreams%20of%20human%20pride%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20not%20a%20worshiper%20of%20royal%20glory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20(mankind)%20are%20the%20essence%20of%20my%20thoughts%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20yours%2C%20my%20loyalty%20is%20not%20for%20the%20exploiters.%E2%80%9D%5D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPravin%20Shakir%E2%80%99s%20powerful%20lament%20against%20oppression%20must%20weigh%20with%20every%20sensitive%20soul%20and%20serves%20as%20an%20inspiration%20for%20our%20collective%20pursuit%20of%20justice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cp%C4%81-ba-gil%20sab%20hai%C3%B1%20rih%C4%81.%C4%AB%20k%C4%A